# ReachBase

> Get paid for your attention on Base.

ReachBase is a decentralized creator monetization and paid messaging platform built on Base. Users set a custom USDC fee for receiving direct messages, allowing creators, founders, developers, investors, recruiters, and professionals to monetize inbound communication.

---

## Features

### Paid Messaging

* Set custom DM fee in USDC
* Instant on-chain payments
* Spam-resistant inbox
* Direct creator monetization

### Creator Profiles

* Wallet-based identity
* Username and bio
* Social links
* Farcaster integration
* Analytics dashboard

### Revenue Dashboard

* Total earnings
* Monthly earnings
* Message volume
* Conversion tracking

### Referral Program

* Referral codes
* Revenue sharing
* Referral leaderboards

### NFT Achievement Badges

* First Paid Message
* 100 Messages
* Top Creator
* Revenue Milestones

### Security

* Smart contract verified payments
* Wallet authentication
* Rate limiting
* Anti-spam protection

