## Database Schema

### Users

```sql
CREATE TABLE users (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 wallet_address TEXT UNIQUE,
 username TEXT UNIQUE,
 bio TEXT,
 avatar TEXT,
 dm_fee NUMERIC,
 earnings NUMERIC DEFAULT 0,
 verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT FALSE,
 created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

### Messages

```sql
CREATE TABLE messages (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 sender TEXT,
 receiver TEXT,
 content TEXT,
 tx_hash TEXT,
 amount NUMERIC,
 status TEXT,
 created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

### Payments

```sql
CREATE TABLE payments (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 sender TEXT,
 receiver TEXT,
 amount NUMERIC,
 platform_fee NUMERIC,
 tx_hash TEXT,
 created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

### Referrals

```sql
CREATE TABLE referrals (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 referrer TEXT,
 referred TEXT,
 commission NUMERIC,
 created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT NOW()
);
```

