## Deployment

### Install

```bash
git clone https://github.com/reachbase/reachbase.git

cd reachbase

npm install
```

### Run

```bash
npm run dev
```

### Deploy Contracts

```bash
npx hardhat run scripts/deploy.ts --network base
```

### Deploy Frontend

```bash
vercel deploy
```

